lead_paragraph: Twelve-year-old Kevin Warren was an aspiring basketball player in the Phoenix area, riding his bike one day when a driver lost control of her car and hit him.

headline.print_headline: For Vikings Executive Kevin Warren, the Work Has Only Begun
